/* Billboard device (display dimension). English; community-refined. */
"Billboard device present" = "Billboard device present";
"A Billboard device is present on this port. That usually appears when an Alt Mode like DisplayPort was set up but didn't fully come up. Your display is below its best mode, so a re-plug, a different cable, or a different adapter may bring it up. Some docks show a Billboard device normally, so this isn't always a fault." = "A Billboard device is present on this port. That usually appears when an Alt Mode like DisplayPort was set up but didn't fully come up. Your display is below its best mode, so a re-plug, a different cable, or a different adapter may bring it up. Some docks show a Billboard device normally, so this isn't always a fault.";

/* Display dimension: compression at the link ceiling (issue #246). */
"Display may be using compression to reach its top mode" = "A tela pode estar usando compressão para alcançar seu modo máximo";
"Your %@ can run %@, which uncompressed would need about %@. This link is already running every lane at a high rate, carrying about %@ (%@). Many high-resolution displays use compression (DSC) to fit their top mode through a link like this, so the link rate alone can't tell whether you're already at your best mode. If the picture looks right, it most likely is." = "Seu %@ pode funcionar a %@, o que sem compressão precisaria de cerca de %@. Este link já usa todas as faixas em alta velocidade e transporta cerca de %@ (%@). Muitas telas de alta resolução usam compressão (DSC) para passar seu modo máximo por um link como este, então a velocidade do link sozinha não diz se você já está no seu melhor modo. Se a imagem parece correta, é muito provável que esteja.";

